headline: Is Global Payments Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: Though Global Payments has lagged behind the S&P 500 Index over the past year, analysts are moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: UK competition watchdog opens formal probe into Global Payments–Worldpay merger
summary: Investing.com -- The UK’s Competition and Markets Authority (CMA) has formally launched an investigation into Global Payments’ planned acquisition of Worldpay.
